Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.26,0:00:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs22\shad1\c&H70D8FB&\fn迷你简汉真广标\b0\pos(312,420)}漫迪字幕组&@Daria拽妹黛薇儿\N\N——·@严肃活泼小kk译制·——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这地方 这是哪?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow, look at this place. I wonder what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是图书馆吧 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}I think it's the library, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}I could have sworn I had money
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我就发誓先把预算留给屋顶翻修\N{\fnArial\fs18}budgeted for a new roof under capital improvements.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都会犯错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, well. Everyone makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那是测谎仪吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Is that a polygraph machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀 抽奖赢回来的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes! Uh, I... won it in a raffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不造到底上哪才能搞来维修费\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't know where we'll get the money for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只能靠募捐啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}A fund-raiser, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,来个70年代"我最摇摆"复古之夜么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Boogie Bash '70s Revival Night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,行不通 迪斯科球被偷了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We can't. Someone stole the disco ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我们得想点别的办法\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, we'll have to come up with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能真正捕捉到朗岱尔高中生精彩生活的好办法\N{\fnArial\fs18}that truly captures the spirit of student life at Lawndale High.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你们觉得为什么...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, why do you think it is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,托尔斯泰认为自己把《战争与和平》写得如此...\N{\fnArial\fs18}that Tolstoy felt he had to make War and Peace so darned...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨人喜欢? Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}unpleasant? Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来就没人逼他写续集了么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So no one would pester him to do a sequel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好呀 祖国的花朵\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good morning, young people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个坏消息要告诉大家\N{\fnArial\fs18}I have a very sad announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,图书馆要关闭一段时间\N{\fnArial\fs18}The library will be closed until further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了 那是我唯一可以独处的好地方\N{\fnArial\fs18}Great. There goes the only place I can go to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛你造那不是真的啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, you know that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为了筹集维修费 学校要搞一个中世纪展会\N{\fnArial\fs18}To raise money for repairs, the school will be presenting a medieval fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,模拟中世纪的生活\N{\fnArial\fs18}simulating life in the middle ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,急招志愿者\N{\fnArial\fs18}Volunteers are desperately needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝做志愿者的人要自愿花10块钱买门票\N{\fnArial\fs18}Those who refuse to volunteer must voluntarily purchase a ticket for ten dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,或自愿接受休学处分\N{\fnArial\fs18}or voluntarily face suspension.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.01,0:02:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,祝大家有个愉快的一天\N{\fnArial\fs18}Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那大概是我听过最逗逼的事了\N{\fnArial\fs18}That may be the stupidest thing I've ever heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我们要参加\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know. We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,北鼻 这对人家来说很重要耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Babe, this is very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,《吉百利故事集》是经典佳作 我觉得我会演的很好\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Cadbury Tales are, like, classic, and I think I'd be great in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就和我一起去试镜嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just do the audition with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 宝贝...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, babe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能把情爱演得和你一样好了 Kevvy\N{\fnArial\fs18}Because nobody plays a love scene like you, Kevvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在去练习吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, go practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命 冲呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, ma'am. Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你的台词\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Wow, where's he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在展会上一起表演戏剧\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're going to be in a play together at the medieval fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh. That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会是最受欢迎的一对\N{\fnArial\fs18}We'll be the most popular ones there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就想嘛 反正我都要当志愿者啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}So I thought, if I have to volunteer anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该也接受青少年该有的挑战\N{\fnArial\fs18}I might as well do something that challenges me as a teen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,也许还能给其他不受欢迎的人的无聊生活增加点乐趣\N{\fnArial\fs18}and maybe bring some joy into the drab lives of others who are less popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 他们会搞一个晚宴剧场 放Ken Barry的戏剧\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, they'll have this dinner theater with a play by this guy, Ken Barry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去给一个超萌的妹妹角色"艾米丽"试镜\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I'm going to audition for "Emily," the really cute sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,"保佑我不受到报复吧..."\N{\fnArial\fs18}"Preserve me from the vengeance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒噢 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's great, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你在展会有什么工作?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, what will you be doing at the fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,负责待在房间里保持距离地观赏\N{\fnArial\fs18}Admiring it from the safe distance of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 这展会挺好的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, this fair is for a very good cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都应该去\N{\fnArial\fs18}Everyone should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈就不用去啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指所有学生\N{\fnArial\fs18}I meant every student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那换梅姑来演咋样?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But what if Meryl Streep here gets the part?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}梅丽尔·斯特里普: 1949年生 好莱坞女演员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么比你和爸在舞台脚灯那拼命喝彩更能表达支持了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nothing says support like you and Dad leading a rousing cheer from the footlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再想想美味的晚宴\N{\fnArial\fs18}And just think of the delicious dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我靠\N{\fnArial\fs18}Huh? Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要去试镜吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Should we try out for the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能还会上海报呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}We might get on a poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得时尚俱乐部不应该参加什么...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't think the Fashion Club should participate in activities
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,被迫交出衣柜自治权的活动\N{\fnArial\fs18}where you surrender wardrobe autonomy to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我们有更重要的事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. We have more important things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去卡仕曼试试亮片礼服呗\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let's go to Cashman's and try on sequined gowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 Sandi Tiffany 猜怎么着?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hi, Sandi, Tiffany. Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你要转学?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're transferring to a new school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我是要给《吉百利故事集》的艾米丽一角试镜\N{\fnArial\fs18}No. I'm trying out for the part of Emily in The Canterbury Tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是奇了个怪啦 我也是\N{\fnArial\fs18}That is so weird. I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...\N{\fnArial\fs18}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是么? 我在报名表上没看到你的名字\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? I didn't see your name on the sign-up sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你要是不想我去就直说\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, if you don't want me to audition then just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,瞎说啥呀 Sandi\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop that foolish talk, Sandi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你去试镜我很开心\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm happy you're auditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你来演就等于我来演嘛 只不过实际上我没演罢了\N{\fnArial\fs18}If you get the part it'll be just like me getting it, only not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,亲们 说了你们也不信\N{\fnArial\fs18}Guys, you're not going to believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Bret Strand刚约我出去了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Bret Strand just asked me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真哒? 你真的没意见么 Quinn?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? Is that okay with you, Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看这先锋派妇产科医生用废弃物创作的高价艺术品\N{\fnArial\fs18}Meet the avant-garde obstetrician who's turned his castoffs into big-ticket artwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来《呕心小世界: 脐带雕塑品 》\N{\fnArial\fs18}Umbilical cord sculpture, next on Sick, Sad World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮个忙么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Could you help me with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的 Quinn 我没钱了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Honestly, Quinn, I'm just tapped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望能帮上忙 可我身无分文\N{\fnArial\fs18}I wish I could, but I'm dead flat broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕我有一快钱 你知道我肯定...\N{\fnArial\fs18}If I had a buck on me, you'd know I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸 我需要有人帮忙排练台词\N{\fnArial\fs18}Da-ad! I need someone to help me rehearse my lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我上大学那会还演过吉尔登斯特恩\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, sure! You know, I played Guildenstern in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}荒诞派代表作《罗森克兰茨和吉尔登斯特恩已死》中的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为自己会紧张 可我镇定自若\N{\fnArial\fs18}I thought I'd be nervous, but I was cool as a cucumber.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那真有趣 因为我只有一点儿...\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's actually interesting because I'm just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我走上舞台 发现自己站在众目睽睽之下\N{\fnArial\fs18}Until I walked on stage and found myself in front of the crowd standing room only.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得太... 太暴露了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I felt so... naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸 你这话一点用都没有\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dad, you're not helping me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我僵住了 一句话都说不出\N{\fnArial\fs18}I froze. I couldn't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,接着大家都在窃笑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then it... started. The snickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的笑声把我轰走了 那些小婊砸\N{\fnArial\fs18}They laughed me off the stage, the jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我去楼上练习\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll go practice upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 亲爱的 其实那也没那么糟糕啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, honey, it wasn't that bad really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嘲笑几个月后就逐渐消停了 而且...\N{\fnArial\fs18}After a few months, the teasing tapered off and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop!
