Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 帕拉蒙 深爱着我的人儿呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Palamon, who has such love for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因此他就... 就该死 真酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}For which he's, like, deserving of death. Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 帕罗曼 谁... 谁能记住这台词呀...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, pal o'mine, who... who... who can remember all this?
