Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, I do, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我宣布你们结为夫妇\N{\fnArial\fs18}I now pronounce you husband and wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,随着幸福的旋律奏起 帕拉蒙与艾米丽成婚\N{\fnArial\fs18}And thus with perfect bliss and melody, Palamon wedded Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拒绝我嘛 小乖乖?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey! Why fight it, toots?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是夫妻了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're man and wife now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,做梦吧 Charles\N{\fnArial\fs18}Keep dreaming, Charles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意 Kevvy... 我是说 帕拉蒙\N{\fnArial\fs18}I do, Kevvy... I mean Palimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也愿意\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我宣布你们...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I now pronounce you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 伙计们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Brittany Brittany? Brittany\N{\fnArial\fs18}um, Brittany. Brittany? Brittany!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,演得... 非常好\N{\fnArial\fs18}That was... very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在该轮到别人试演了\N{\fnArial\fs18}But now it's time to give someone else a chance to audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好哒 走吧 Kevvy\N{\fnArial\fs18}Okay. Come on, Kevvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其实呢 我想让Kevin留在台上\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, actually, I'd like Kevin to stay on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin 你演得确实不错\N{\fnArial\fs18}Kevin, you're really doing something special with Palamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可是... 我不就是帕拉蒙吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But... aren't I Palamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 下一个演艾米丽的是谁?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, who's next for Emily?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn Quinn Morgendorffer\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ah, Quinn. Quinn Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会为自己编一个精致的花环 并放声歌唱 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs18}♪ I will make a dainty garland for my head and sing. ♪
