Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会为自己编一个精致的花环 并放声歌唱 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs18}♪ I will make a dainty garland for my head and sing. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哼着小调 哒啦哒啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}With a hey-nonny-nonny, tra-la, tra-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你能消停会不?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Would you give it a rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 我要排练\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria, I have to rehearse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈让你来的 不赖我\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not my fault Mom's making you come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有让你来呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's not like I want you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Aw, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩别吵了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn Daria很开心能看你表演呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn, Daria's very happy to be seeing you in your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧 Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Aren't you, Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我会为自己编个精致的花环 并勒脖自尽\N{\fnArial\fs18}I will make a dainty garland for my neck and choke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望其他女孩不会因为你得到这角色而失落\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hope the other girls weren't too disappointed that you got the part over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看 Sandi就没什么意见\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, let's see. Sandi was really nice about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她说她老了\N{\fnArial\fs18}She said she's too mature
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,才不会嫉妒别人那无与伦比 难以置信又名不副实的运气\N{\fnArial\fs18}to get upset at somebody else's incredible, unbelievable, undeserved luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Brittany就嘟囔了几句\N{\fnArial\fs18}And Brittany just kind of made noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜她为你和Kevin一起表演这事\N{\fnArial\fs18}I guess she's speechless with joy that you and Kevin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,开心到说不出话了\N{\fnArial\fs18}are going to be acting together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,奉告一句 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs18}For your information, Daria,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她自愿接送Kevin 好让他背下台词\N{\fnArial\fs18}she volunteered to drive him so he could work on his lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她有没有自愿给Kevin做个精巧的脑移植手术\N{\fnArial\fs18}Did she volunteer to get him a dainty transplant for his head
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好让他背下台词?\N{\fnArial\fs18}so he could remember them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,熊孩子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老不死\N{\fnArial\fs18}Crazy old jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望那没让你分神\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hope that didn't disturb your concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fnArial\fs18}Nah. I'm cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的 我不想让任何事打扰你\N{\fnArial\fs18}'Cause, you know, I don't want anything to distract you from your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我造 谢谢宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know, babe. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝... 那不是去学校的岔道么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, babe... isn't that the turnoff for school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢\N{\fnArial\fs18}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗? 哇 我真的很专心致志耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? Wow. I am concentrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria? Quinn?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Daria? Quinn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 他们刚还在这\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's funny, they were here a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 亲 帽子上的尾巴不错嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, my man! Cool threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我没用?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You calling me a wuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda Tom\N{\fnArial\fs18}Linda! Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Helen. Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们见过Sam和Chris了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Have you met Sam and Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们 向Morgendorffer夫妇问好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Boys, say hello to Mr. and Mrs. Morgendorffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾 废柴\N{\fnArial\fs18}You suck. You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们 快回来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh, kids, come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜Quinn能参演主角\N{\fnArial\fs18}Congratulations on Quinn getting the lead in the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 我听说竞争很激烈\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why, thank you. I heard the competition was pretty stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的Sandi演得不怎样\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, poor Sandi's acting is a little subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显 O'Neill老师要挑最优秀的人\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mr. O'Neill was obviously looking for someone over the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,White同学 如果你能在这签名同意任何意外死亡...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Mr. White, if you'll just sign this waiver absolving Lawndale High
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,都与朗岱尔高中无关 我们就能开始啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}of any responsibility for your accidental death, we can start the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛开始\N{\fnArial\fs18}Let the sport begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叫Jamie的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, if it isn't Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你挥杆挥得比翻书好\N{\fnArial\fs18}I hope you're better at wielding a lance than you are at opening a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你说对了我的名字 有人还叫过我...\N{\fnArial\fs18}You got my name right. Somebody actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位\N{\fnArial\fs18}Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你过来陪我\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks for meeting me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我本来就打算来的嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, I wanted to come, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再说我得离开家 Trent掌握了新的弦乐\N{\fnArial\fs18}Besides, I had to get out. Trent discovered a new chord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位小可爱对牧歌有兴趣?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Would either of you lovelies be interested in a madrigal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呸\N{\fnArial\fs18}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是勇敢的Chuck大人 Chuck大人阳刚威猛 四肢发达...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I am the brave Sir Chuck, Sir Chuck, manly and strong and quick...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你舌头割下来 舌头割下来 用棍子加以翻炒\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'm going to cut out your tongue, your tongue, and fry it up on a stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴贱死了 嘿 Andrea 你喜欢牧歌么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Feisty. Hey! Andrea! You like madrigals?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}五十年代经典儿童木偶剧《胡迪嘟迪秀》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我 和胡迪都迪没两样的变态\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't touch me, you Howdy-Doody-looking creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,下午好 小伙子们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Good afternoon, young men.
