Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是"技能游戏"才对\N{\fnArial\fs18}Maybe I should say games of skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老天 Stacy 咋了? 你看起来很糟\N{\fnArial\fs18}God, Stacy, what's wrong? You look awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah. Really, really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是Bret 第一次约会后他说他会打给我 可他一直没打\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's Bret. He said he'd call me after our first date but he never did,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚看到他了 我和他打招呼 可他装作没看到\N{\fnArial\fs18}and I just saw him and I said hi and he pretended like he didn't even see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真惨\N{\fnArial\fs18}Bummer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着长裙好难走路\N{\fnArial\fs18}These long skirts are so hard to walk in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stacy 会好起来的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stacy, it's gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他不值得 男人都这德性\N{\fnArial\fs18}He's not worth it. No guy is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有闺蜜可以依靠真好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, it's so great to know I can count on my true friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那他现在没有和别人约会?\N{\fnArial\fs18}So, then, he's not dating anyone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信Quinn能超越你 拿到角色\N{\fnArial\fs18}I cannot believe Quinn got the part over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无真材实料\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信她会演得很好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, I'm sure she'll do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得被万人迷吻了 你会从噩梦中醒来?\N{\fnArial\fs18}If Prince Charming kisses you, you think you'll wake up from this nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这有理有据 好么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's for a good cause, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直这样给自己洗脑\N{\fnArial\fs18}You just keep telling yourself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,或者让宫女来给你洗脑\N{\fnArial\fs18}Or have your ladies-in-waiting do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mack王子在哪?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Where's Prince Mack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是Barch老师的主意\N{\fnArial\fs18}It was Ms. Barch's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你是班尼龙?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you Barney?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}Barney是美国少儿节目 主角为紫色玩具小恐龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}占卜未来 女生2刀 男生20刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了那龙 杀了那龙\N{\fnArial\fs18}Kill the dragon! Kill the dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你会在青春期结婚\N{\fnArial\fs18}You will marry a man while still in your prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,学生时代过后\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then, after putting him through school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,花20年求他放弃该死的球员身份\N{\fnArial\fs18}and spending 20 long-suffering years begging him to turn off those damn Broncos
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}Broncos丹佛野马 职业美式足球球队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,找点正经事干 结果他拍屁股走人\N{\fnArial\fs18}and get a real job, he'll walk out of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}原意: 在干净的地毯后边留下一串泥泞的脚印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,留下一堆烂摊子\N{\fnArial\fs18}leaving a trail of muddy footprints behind on the freshly cleaned carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可没有他你会过得更好 更加好\N{\fnArial\fs18}But you'll be better off without him. Much better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,更加更加好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Much, much better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是个活生生的例子\N{\fnArial\fs18}And she's the living proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也去预测未来呗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Should we get our fortunes read?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不去 感知当下就已经够糟糕了\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll pass. Knowing the present is bad enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那坐坐摩天轮?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then how about a Ferris wheel ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我有没有很痛不欲生?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do I look desperate to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}罗马天主教势力与西欧封建主对穆斯林发动的侵略战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,十字军东征\N{\fnArial\fs18}Crusades! Crusades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们... 听我唱一首《被误解的吟游诗人》\N{\fnArial\fs18}Ladies... wait till you hear the Ballad of the Misunderstood Minstrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我看起来痛不欲生了吧?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Do I look desperate to you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 的确 - 走吧\N{\fnArial\fs18}- Yep. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们太幸运了 还剩一个位置\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're in luck. One basket left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 快来听听我的歌\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, come on. Listen to my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是12行诗\N{\fnArial\fs18}It's only got 12 verses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,审判到了 审判到了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Inquisition! Inquisition!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托拜托 你让我上去嘛\N{\fnArial\fs18}Please, you gotta let me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 没位了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Can't. We're full up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可我不想让别人看到我的眼睛\N{\fnArial\fs18}But I don't want anyone to see my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,都红成这样了\N{\fnArial\fs18}They're this really weird shade of red.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 出于安全考虑...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sorry, safety regulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我付双倍的钱\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll pay you double.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全员登陆\N{\fnArial\fs18}All aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 你不能这样安排\N{\fnArial\fs18}Excuse me. You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是人类 妈蛋\N{\fnArial\fs18}We're human beings, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都以为我当时是剖腹产\N{\fnArial\fs18}And everyone thought I'd had a cesarean
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为Sandi的头型很圆润\N{\fnArial\fs18}because Sandi's head was so round and smooth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不像其他小孩那样扁平多棱角\N{\fnArial\fs18}and not flat and bumpy like the other babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只用了两小时二十分钟就把Quinn生出来了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, my labor with Quinn was only two hours, 20 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她脑袋也很圆\N{\fnArial\fs18}so her head was quite round, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:14:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好 过35岁才生孩子的风险特高\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's great, especially since giving birth can be risky for women over 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我想让大家花一分钟设想一下观众的反应\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, I want everyone to take a minute and visualize the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,当戏剧完美谢幕\N{\fnArial\fs18}As we finish our wonderful play,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们品尝完美味的晚宴后起立鼓掌\N{\fnArial\fs18}they finish their delicious dinner and leap up as one in a standing ovation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,精妙绝伦 大家太棒啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Brava! Brava! Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,精妙绝伦 精妙绝伦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Brava, brava!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 低下头来缅怀可怜的詹姆斯·迪恩\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, let's bow our heads for a moment and remember poor James Dean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}著名电影演员 美国十大文化偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 帕拉蒙 深爱着我的人儿呀\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, Palamon, who has such love for me;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我会为自己编一个精致的花环...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I will make a dainty garland...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandi? Tiffany? 你们来干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Sandi? Tiffany? What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来祝你好运\N{\fnArial\fs18}We came by to wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你应该用不着\N{\fnArial\fs18}Not that you'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,用不着\N{\fnArial\fs18}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真哒?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你很有天赋 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs18}You're really talented, Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我特别欣赏你独特的影响力\N{\fnArial\fs18}I especially like your unique inflections.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,比如 给我们说句台词\N{\fnArial\fs18}Like, say a line for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, okay:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"我会为自己编一个精致的花环 并放声歌唱"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"I will make a dainty garland for my head and sing."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,懂我说的么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}See what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,懂什么 Sandi?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you mean, Sandi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人会这么说\N{\fnArial\fs18}Well, anybody else would have said
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"我会为自己编一个精致的花环"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"I will make a dainty garland for my head."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可你嘛 Quinn 凭你..精湛的演技 你是这么说的\N{\fnArial\fs18}But you, Quinn, with your... special talent, you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"我会为自己编一个精致的花环 并放声歌唱"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"I will make a dainty garland for my head."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你肯定很有天赋\N{\fnArial\fs18}I mean, it must be talent
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你不会重读错单词嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs18}because you wouldn't emphasize the wrong words, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不会\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得咯\N{\fnArial\fs18}I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信她觉得自己能在选角上拼过你\N{\fnArial\fs18}I can't believe she thinks she should have gotten the part over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无真材实料\N{\fnArial\fs18}That's so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 看见Kevin了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Quinn? Have you seen Kevin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 我知道我们上学不用走高速\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, I know we don't take a highway to school, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um... no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,人家甚至穿了破洞的天鹅绒背心 还是低胸的\N{\fnArial\fs18}I even wore my crushed velvet tank top, the one with the scoop neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可他还是没再约我出去\N{\fnArial\fs18}and he still didn't ask me out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你们人缘好就会明白的\N{\fnArial\fs18}If only you were popular enough to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对 要是呗\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, if only.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这破摩天轮什么时候才能停?\N{\fnArial\fs18}When the hell is this ride going to be over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,晚宴剧场 这是晚饭\N{\fnArial\fs18}Dinner theater; this is dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没有餐具?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Don't we get utensils?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 这是中世纪 老爷子\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, it's the middle ages, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,老爷子?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Pops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,走啦 Jake\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜这火鸡剩下的部分去哪了?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What do you think happened to the rest of this turkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,试着把这赖到"读写困难"头上\N{\fnArial\fs18}Try blaming this on dyslexia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 反正Quinn的戏剧马上就要开始了\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, Quinn's play's about to start, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位\N{\fnArial\fs18}Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可为毛? 是因为我说的话么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}But why? Is it something I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的穿着么? 我还是死了罢\N{\fnArial\fs18}Something I wore? Oh, I wish I were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 别因为些屌丝不再约你\N{\fnArial\fs18}Look, don't flush your entire world down the drain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就自甘堕落\N{\fnArial\fs18}just because some jerk didn't ask you out on a second date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可能压根不是你的错\N{\fnArial\fs18}It probably had nothing to do with you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你真的做了蠢事\N{\fnArial\fs18}Unless you did something really stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,比如拿你的小问题和复杂的脑洞去烦他\N{\fnArial\fs18}like bore him with your petty problems and convoluted logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会那样做?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这真恶心 我快吐了\N{\fnArial\fs18}This is revolting. I think I'm going to be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真的吃那玩意?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hey, you going to eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会编一个精致的花环\N{\fnArial\fs18}I will make a dainty garland!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我会编一个精致的花环 我会编...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I will make a dainty garland. I will make...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 Quinn 我就来给你打打气\N{\fnArial\fs18}Hi, Quinn. I just wanted to stop buy and wish you good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你鼓鼓劲\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to wish you even better luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你加加油\N{\fnArial\fs18}I want to wish you the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,想帮忙的话就把Kevin找回来\N{\fnArial\fs18}Guys, if you want to help me, find Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在这 没人演帕拉蒙\N{\fnArial\fs18}He's not here and there's no one to play Palamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我来演帕拉蒙...\N{\fnArial\fs18}I'll play Palamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fnArial\fs18}Come on, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我来演\N{\fnArial\fs18}No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别再为人家撕逼了啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Guys, don't fight over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,非常时期需要非常手段\N{\fnArial\fs18}Desperate times call for desperate measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}一种点人的童谣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,点指兵兵 点到谁人做大兵\N{\fnArial\fs18}Eeny-meeny-miny-mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就你了 Jeffy 你只要念出帕拉蒙的台词就好\N{\fnArial\fs18}Now, Jeffy, all you have to do is read Palamon's lines
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,直到Kevin过来解释他为什么缺席\N{\fnArial\fs18}until Kevin gets here with his very good reason for sabotaging our play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢啦 Jeffy\N{\fnArial\fs18}Thanks, Jeffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我该演谁来着?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who am I supposed to be again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个叫P什么的?\N{\fnArial\fs18}It started with a "P"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,赎罪者\N{\fnArial\fs18}The Pardoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"我会为自己编一个精致的花环 并放声歌唱"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"I will make a dainty garland for my head and sing."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:18:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"欲望源自醉意"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"That lust proceeds from wine and drunkenness,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"考虑到酒后乱性有多反常..."\N{\fnArial\fs18}consider how drunken Lot pervertedly slept with..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"欲望源自醉意"\N{\fnArial\fs18}"That lust proceeds from..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fnArial\fs18}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都在窃笑 马勒戈壁\N{\fnArial\fs18}Snicker, snicker, snicker! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在笑? 特么有那么好笑吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Who's laughing? What's so damn funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你这小...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why you little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?\N{\fnArial\fs18}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那你觉得我该打给他吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Then, do you think I should call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 现在就打 好防止我去正当杀人\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yes, right now. Before I commit justifiable homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,绝逼热脸贴冷屁股\N{\fnArial\fs18}Must-stick-head-cold-water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,亲 能帮帮忙么?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Guys, can you help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,演练厅有点混乱\N{\fnArial\fs18}There's some kind of riot going on in the auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我看会咨询摊 我去找李校长\N{\fnArial\fs18}Just watch the information booth while I find Ms. Li.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 我俩现在身负重任\N{\fnArial\fs18}Uh-oh, someone just put us in a position of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今天突然变得邪恶起来啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}The day has suddenly turned sinister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想让戏剧成功出演\N{\fnArial\fs18}I just wanted the play to go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当然啦\N{\fnArial\fs18}Of course you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 在另一世 你是女人 这就是你为嘛这么多愁善感\N{\fnArial\fs18}See, in another life, you were a woman, which explains why you have feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你抽的牌还说\N{\fnArial\fs18}Your cards also say that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你能和一个风韵犹存的同事共享天伦之乐\N{\fnArial\fs18}you and a still-attractive coworker have a chance for unparalleled bliss,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这能让你避免因性别相同而过穴居生活\N{\fnArial\fs18}provided you avoid the troglodytic behavior common to your sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真的? 何时?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Really? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很快\N{\fnArial\fs18}Very, very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么不穿戏服?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Why aren't you wearing costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们穿了\N{\fnArial\fs18}We were,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不过把它们捐给中世纪美化暴力博物馆了\N{\fnArial\fs18}but we donated them to the Museum of Glorifying Violence In Medieval Times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,中世纪酷酷哒\N{\fnArial\fs18}The medieval times were cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,空气更清新 也没那么拥挤\N{\fnArial\fs18}Yeah, the air was cleaner and there was less crowding
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,自从黑死病消灭了许多地方三分之一的人口\N{\fnArial\fs18}since the Black Death wiped out a third of the population in many places.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,看到街上有牛车开过也是蛮酷\N{\fnArial\fs18}Must have been cool to see the ox carts rolling through the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,塞满了腐烂中的尸体\N{\fnArial\fs18}piled high with festering corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,罗宾汉其实活在14世纪\N{\fnArial\fs18}And the real Robin Hood actually lived in the 1300s.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,国王爱德华二世搜捕了罗宾汉非法偷猎的鹿群\N{\fnArial\fs18}King Edward II busted Robin and his band of outlaws poaching deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 罗宾汉没有受到惩罚\N{\fnArial\fs18}But, rather than punish him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爱德华赦免了罗宾汉 二人结为基友\N{\fnArial\fs18}he pardoned Robin and made him his special friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,罗宾汉很感激 从那天开始他就坚持替国王洗澡澡\N{\fnArial\fs18}Robin was so grateful, from that day on he insisted on giving the king his bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\an8}英王亨利八世第二任妻子 伊丽莎白一世的生母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上 安娜·波莲也不漂亮\N{\fnArial\fs18}Actually, Anne Boleyn was no prize either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她左手长了六根手指 脖子上还有大瘤子\N{\fnArial\fs18}She had six fingers on her left hand, a big mole on her neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别问我瘤子下边怎么了\N{\fnArial\fs18}and don't even ask me what was going on below that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝...\N{\fnArial\fs18}Um, babe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我知道开去学校用不了这么长时间\N{\fnArial\fs18}now, I know it doesn't take this long to drive to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定?\N{\fnArial\fs18}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fnArial\fs18}Oh, man!
